{
  "texts": [
    "Once the operation completes, the thread injects the IRQ to notify the guest driver to resume execution.",
    "This optimizes parallel request processing such that the maximum number of concurrent threads equals the number of ranks for the virtual machine.AVX512 and C enhancements in Firecracker.",
    "Firecracker is developed in Rust.",
    "While generally does not impact performance.",
    "However, vPIM implementation benefit from rewriting specific code sections in C. We use a C implementation of AVX instructions and matrix management in the read-from-rank and write-to-rank operations."
  ]
}